## Description {#details}

An iterator over specifically call edges.

This has the same iteration properties as the <code>iterator</code>, but restricts itself to edges which represent actual calls.

Definition at line 220 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/analysis/lazycallgraph-h">LazyCallGraph.h</a>.
